@page
@model DashboardModel
@{ViewData["Title"]="Results Dashboard";var p=Model.Results.Predictive;var c=Model.Results.Causal;}
<h1>Results dashboard</h1><p class="lede">Frozen locked-test prediction metrics and protocol-defined observational estimates.</p><h2>Predictive performance</h2><div class="metrics"><partial name="_Metric" model='("ROC AUC",p.RocAuc.ToString("F4"))'/><partial name="_Metric" model='("PR AUC",p.PrAuc.ToString("F4"))'/><partial name="_Metric" model='("Log loss",p.LogLoss.ToString("F4"))'/><partial name="_Metric" model='("Brier",p.BrierScore.ToString("F4"))'/><partial name="_Metric" model='("Precision",p.Precision.ToString("F4"))'/><partial name="_Metric" model='("Recall",p.Recall.ToString("F4"))'/><partial name="_Metric" model='("F1",p.F1.ToString("F4"))'/><partial name="_Metric" model='("Specificity",p.Specificity.ToString("F4"))'/></div>
<h2>Causal findings</h2><div class="metrics"><partial name="_Metric" model='(".NET AIPW ATT",c.Aipw.ToString("F5"))'/><partial name="_Metric" model='("95% CI",$"{c.ConfidenceLower:F5} to {c.ConfidenceUpper:F5}")'/><partial name="_Metric" model='("IPTW",c.Iptw.ToString("F5"))'/><partial name="_Metric" model='("Outcome regression",c.OutcomeRegression.ToString("F6"))'/><partial name="_Metric" model='("Unadjusted",c.Unadjusted.ToString("F5"))'/><partial name="_Metric" model='("Python cross-fitted",c.PythonAipw.ToString("F5"))'/></div><aside>The confidence interval includes zero. The analysis did not provide clear evidence of a nonzero causal effect under the stated observational assumptions, and does not establish that neighboring-state adoption causes adoption.</aside>
